### Upload une image
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/media
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="gateau.jpg"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-images/gateau.png
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isFeatured"

true
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Upload une vidéo
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/media
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="video.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./test-videos/video.mp4
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="altText"

Vidéo de démonstration du gâteau
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Upload multiple (images + vidéos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/media/multiple
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="image1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/image1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="video1.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< ./test-videos/video1.mp4
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### Récupérer les media d'un produit
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/media

### Produit avec ses media
